          "Flag",
          "Anthem: ليبيا، ليبيا، ليبيا \" Libya, Libya, Libya \"",
          "Show globe Show map of Libya",
          "^ United Nations note concerning official name: \"Following the adoption by the General Assembly of resolution 66/1, the Permanent Mission of Libya to the United Nations formally notified the United Nations of a Declaration by the National Transitional Council of 3 August changing the official name of the Libyan Arab Jamahiriya to 'Libya' and changing Libya's national flag.\" ^ The official language is simply identified as \" Arabic \" ( Constitutional Declaration , article 1). ^ The UK and France held a joint condominium over Libya through the United Nations Trusteeship Council ."
